erfect score on the first try, don’t worry.  You can take the Millsberry Astronomy Challenge as many times as you need until you get 100%.<BR><BR>All set?  Then just click <A HREF='/academy/lab/trivia.phtml?st=1'>Play</A> to go right to the game!  </FONT></TD></TR><TR HEIGHT='33'><TD ALIGN='CENTER' WIDTH='33%'>&nbsp;</TD><TD ALIGN='CENTER' WIDTH='33%'><A HREF='/academy/lab/trivia.phtml?st=1'><IMG SRC='http://www.millsberry.com/images/site_gfx/play.gif' BORDER='0' onMouseOver="src='http://www.millsberry.com/images/site_gfx/play_over.gif';" onMouseOut="src='http://www.millsberry.com/images/site_gfx/play.gif';" onMouseDown="src='http://www.millsberry.com/images/site_gfx/play_down.gif';"></A></TD><TD ALIGN='CENTER' WIDTH='33%'><A HREF='/academy/lab/trivia.phtml?intro=1'><IMG SRC='http://www.millsberry.com/images/site_gfx/next.gif' BORDER='0' onMouseOver="src='http://www.millsberry.com/images/site_gfx/next_over.gif';" onMouseOut="src='http://www.millsberry.com/images/site_gfx/next.gif';" onMouseDown="src='http://www.millsberry.com/images/site_gfx/next_down.gif';"></A></TD></TR><TR HEIGHT='5'><TD COLSPAN='3'></TD></TR></TABLE></TD><TD><IMG SRC='http://www.millsberry.com/images/site_gfx/site_images/trivia_right.gif' WIDTH='37' HEIGHT='416'></TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN='3'><IMG SRC='http://www.millsberry.com/images/site_gfx/site_images/trivia_bottom.gif' WIDTH='500' HEIGHT='37'></TD></TR></TABLE></BODY></HTML>